#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "makeshift wooden cuirass"
msgid_plural "makeshift wooden cuirasses"
msgstr[0] "臨時木製胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift wooden cuirass', 'str_pl': 'makeshift
#. wooden cuirasses'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift wooden cuirass, actually just a bunch of boards fastened "
"somewhat tight with strings."
msgstr "一件臨時木製胸甲，實際上只是幾塊木板用繩子勉強綁緊。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "elaborate wooden cuirass"
msgid_plural "elaborate wooden cuirasses"
msgstr[0] "精製木製胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'elaborate wooden cuirass', 'str_pl': 'elaborate
#. wooden cuirasses'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"An elaborate wooden cuirass, more thin, flexible and with shoulderpads for "
"better coverage."
msgstr "一件精製木製胸甲，更薄、更靈活，並帶有肩甲以提供更好的覆蓋。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wooden laminar cuirass"
msgid_plural "wooden laminar cuirasses"
msgstr[0] "木製層壓胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden laminar cuirass', 'str_pl': 'wooden
#. laminar cuirasses'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"An armor made from thin wooden sheets with carefully cut grooves sewn onto a"
" cloth undershirt."
msgstr "一種由薄木片製成的盔甲，帶有精心切割的凹槽，縫在布質內衣上。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wooden laminar suit"
msgid_plural "wooden laminar suits"
msgstr[0] "木製層壓套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden laminar suit'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A suit of armor made from thin wooden sheets with carefully cut grooves sewn"
" onto a cloth gambeson."
msgstr "一套由薄木片製成的盔甲，帶有精心切割的凹槽，縫在布質軟甲上。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wire mail shirt"
msgid_plural "wire mail shirts"
msgstr[0] "線編鎖子襯衫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wire mail shirt'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A shirt made out of wires, coiled around and sewn into fabric. Not even "
"close to a proper mail, but better than just clothing."
msgstr "一件用線材製成的襯衫，纏繞並縫入織物中。遠不及真正的鎖子甲，但比普通衣物要好。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wire mail sleeves"
msgid_plural "wire mail sleevess"
msgstr[0] "線編鎖子護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wire mail sleeves'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of sleeves made out of wires, coiled around and sewn into fabric. "
"Sacrifices coverage to leave the elbow unencumbered. Not even close to a "
"proper mail, but better than just clothing."
msgstr "一對用線材製成的護臂，纏繞並縫入織物中。犧牲覆蓋範圍以保持肘部不受阻礙。遠不及真正的鎖子甲，但比普通衣物要好。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wire mail leggins"
msgid_plural "wire mail legginss"
msgstr[0] "線編鎖子護腿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wire mail leggins'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of leggins made out of wires, coiled around and sewn into fabric. "
"Sacrifices coverage to leave the knee unencumbered. Not even close to a "
"proper mail, but better than just clothing."
msgstr "一對用線材製成的護腿，纏繞並縫入織物中。犧牲覆蓋範圍以保持膝部不受阻礙。遠不及真正的鎖子甲，但比普通衣物要好。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wooden helmet"
msgid_plural "wooden helmets"
msgstr[0] "木製頭盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden helmet'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift wooden helmet. Heavy, uncomfortable and not quite sturdy, "
"because the pieces are held together with a glue. "
msgstr "一頂臨時木製頭盔。沉重、不舒適且不太堅固，因為部件是用膠水粘合的。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "bottle vambraces"
msgid_plural "bottle vambracess"
msgstr[0] "瓶制護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bottle vambraces'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"Have a spare bottle? Cut it in half, stuff inside some padding, fasten it "
"with rags or string and use as vambraces. Hey, it's better than nothing."
msgstr "有多餘的瓶子嗎？把它切成兩半，塞進一些填充物，用破布或繩子固定，當作護臂用。嘿，總比沒有好。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "plastic breastplate"
msgid_plural "plastic breastplates"
msgstr[0] "塑料胸板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plastic breastplate'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift plastic breastplate with some padding. Not as good as factory-"
"made football armor, but it's way less bulky and covers more torso area."
msgstr "一件帶有填充物的臨時塑料胸板。不如工廠製造的美式足球護甲好，但遠沒有那麼笨重，並且覆蓋更多的軀幹區域。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "plastic sheath"
msgid_plural "plastic sheathes"
msgstr[0] "塑料鞘"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'plastic sheath', 'str_pl': 'plastic
#. sheathes'}.
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "You sheath your %s"
msgstr "你將你的%s收鞘。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'plastic sheath', 'str_pl':
#. 'plastic sheathes'}.
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "Sheath knife"
msgstr "收鞘刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plastic sheath', 'str_pl': 'plastic sheathes'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A plastic sheath with a fastening strap and using rags as inner padding. A "
"bit more clumsy to use than the regular sheath. Activate to sheathe/draw a "
"weapon."
msgstr "一個帶有固定帶並使用破布作為內襯的塑料鞘。比普通鞘使用起來稍顯笨拙。激活以收鞘/拔出武器。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "tin can vambraces"
msgid_plural "tin can vambracess"
msgstr[0] "錫罐護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tin can vambraces'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A pair of tin cans with removed bottoms and cut open along the side to allow"
" wearing them on wrists. Some rags are wrapped around the sharp sides and to"
" hold it firmly."
msgstr "一對去掉底部並沿側面切開以便戴在手腕上的錫罐。尖銳的邊緣用破布包裹並固定牢固。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "linothorax"
msgid_plural "linothoraxes"
msgstr[0] "亞麻胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'linothorax', 'str_pl': 'linothoraxes'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A semi-historical(it would be neat to add small pockets) replica of "
"linothorax. Strong, light and comfortable; it has only one flaw - it will "
"fall apart under the rain, and the only way of waterproofing you can think "
"of is the beeswax. "
msgstr "一件半歷史（如果能加上小口袋就更好了）的亞麻胸甲複製品。堅固、輕便且舒適；它只有一個缺點——在雨中會散架，而你能想到的唯一防水方法是蜂蠟。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "sandbag vest"
msgid_plural "sandbag vests"
msgstr[0] "沙袋背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sandbag vest'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A vest with dozens of sand-filled pockets. Kinda prone to ripping, and when "
"it happens the sand disperses, making it impossible to repair, only make a "
"new one."
msgstr "一件帶有數十個裝滿沙子的口袋的背心。比較容易撕裂，一旦撕裂沙子就會散落，導致無法修復，只能重新制作一件。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "cardboard visor"
msgid_plural "cardboard visors"
msgstr[0] "紙板遮陽帽簷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cardboard visor'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "A cardboard visor. Protects from sun glare."
msgstr "一個紙板遮陽帽簷。能防止陽光刺眼。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wooden scale cuirass"
msgid_plural "wooden scale cuirasses"
msgstr[0] "木鱗胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden scale cuirass', 'str_pl': 'wooden scale
#. cuirasses'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"An armor made from wooden scales with carefully drilled holes sewn onto a "
"cloth undershirt."
msgstr "一件由木鱗片製成的盔甲，上面有精心鑽出的孔，縫在布質內衣上。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wooden scale suit"
msgid_plural "wooden scale suits"
msgstr[0] "木鱗套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden scale suit'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A suit of armor made from wooden scales with carefully drilled holes sewn "
"onto a cloth gambeson."
msgstr "一套由木鱗片製成的盔甲，上面有精心鑽出的孔，縫在布質棉甲上。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "makeshift metal skullcap"
msgid_plural "makeshift metal skullcaps"
msgstr[0] "臨時金屬無邊帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift metal skullcap'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "A skullcap hammered out of metal sheet."
msgstr "一頂用金屬板敲打製成的無邊帽。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "metal sheet vest"
msgid_plural "metal sheet vests"
msgstr[0] "金屬板背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'metal sheet vest'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A vest with two thin, but nevertheless inflexible metal sheets sealed inside"
" its big pockets."
msgstr "一件背心，其大口袋內封有兩片薄但堅硬的金屬板。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "blanket poncho"
msgid_plural "blanket ponchos"
msgstr[0] "毯子斗篷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blanket poncho'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A blanket with a hole for the head and a belt. Less encumbering to wear, but"
" also less warm."
msgstr "一條帶有頭部開口和腰帶的毯子。穿著時負擔較輕，但保暖性也較差。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wooden mask"
msgid_plural "wooden masks"
msgstr[0] "木面具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden mask'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "A plain wooden mask. Looks kinda... creepy."
msgstr "一個樸素的木面具。看起來有點……詭異。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "tire arm guards"
msgid_plural "tire arm guardss"
msgstr[0] "輪胎護臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tire arm guards'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "A pair of arm guards cut from a thick motorbike tire."
msgstr "一副用厚摩托車輪胎切割製成的護臂。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "tire leg guards"
msgid_plural "tire leg guardss"
msgstr[0] "輪胎護腿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tire leg guards'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "A pair of leg guards cut from a thick automobile tire."
msgstr "一副用厚汽車輪胎切割製成的護腿。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wire holster"
msgid_plural "wire holsters"
msgstr[0] "鐵絲槍套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wire holster'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"Also called coat hanger or jamaican holster, this is just a piece of wire "
"with one end going into a barrel and the other one belted to pants. For "
"small firearms only."
msgstr "也被稱為衣架或牙買加槍套，這只是一根鐵絲，一端插入槍管，另一端系在褲子上。僅適用於小型槍械。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "patchwork pants"
msgid_plural "pants"
msgstr[0] "拼布褲子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'patchwork pants', 'str_pl': 'pants'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "A pair of makeshift patchwork pants. "
msgstr "一條臨時拼布褲子。"

#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid "wicker shield"
msgid_plural "wicker shields"
msgstr[0] "柳條盾牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wicker shield'}
#: .\mod_armor.json
msgid ""
"A wicker shield, used by light infantry and skirmishers in antiquity and by "
"various indigenous tribes."
msgstr "一面柳條盾牌，古代輕步兵和散兵以及各種土著部落使用。"

#: .\mod_items.json
msgid "makeshift raft"
msgid_plural "makeshift rafts"
msgstr[0] "臨時木筏"

#. ~ Use action unfold_msg for {'str': 'makeshift raft'}.
#: .\mod_items.json
msgid "You unfold the %s."
msgstr "你展開了%s。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift raft'}
#: .\mod_items.json
msgid ""
"This is a primitive raft folded in half for storage. (A)ctivate to unfold "
"and place it."
msgstr "這是一個為便於儲存而摺疊成兩半的原始木筏。(A)ctivate以展開並放置它。"

#: .\mod_items.json
msgid "makeshift canoe"
msgid_plural "makeshift canoes"
msgstr[0] "臨時獨木舟"

#. ~ Use action unfold_msg for {'str': 'makeshift canoe'}.
#: .\mod_items.json
msgid "You place the %s."
msgstr "你放置了%s。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift canoe'}
#: .\mod_items.json
msgid ""
"This is a dugout canoe hollowed out of tree trunk. (A)ctivate to place it."
msgstr "這是一艘由樹幹挖空製成的獨木舟。(A)激活以放置。"

#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "makeshift mace"
msgid_plural "makeshift maces"
msgstr[0] "臨時狼牙棒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift mace'}
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift mace. You cannot think of any fancy techniques you may use with "
"it, but it's rather compact and gets the job done."
msgstr "一把臨時狼牙棒。你想不出能用它施展什麼花哨技巧，但它相當緊湊且能完成任務。"

#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "crude dagger"
msgid_plural "crude daggers"
msgstr[0] "粗製匕首"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crude dagger'}
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid ""
"A crude and thick welded dagger with a sharpened point suitable only for "
"combat. "
msgstr "一把粗厚焊接的匕首，帶有僅適用於戰鬥的鋒利尖端。"

#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "crude mace"
msgid_plural "crude maces"
msgstr[0] "粗製狼牙棒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crude mace'}
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid ""
"A crude welded mace. You cannot think of any fancy techniques you may use "
"with it, but it's rather compact and gets the job done."
msgstr "一把粗製焊接的狼牙棒。你想不出能用它施展什麼花哨技巧，但它相當緊湊且能完成任務。"

#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "wooden pike"
msgid_plural "wooden pikes"
msgstr[0] "木製長矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wooden pike'}
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid ""
"A long wooden pike with a fire-hardened point. Quite sturdy because of its "
"thickness, this weapon is more suited to supporting others, fighting in "
"formation and defending on rough terrain. "
msgstr "一柄帶有火硬化尖端的長木矛。因其厚度相當堅固，這種武器更適合支援他人、在陣型中作戰以及在崎嶇地形上防禦。"

#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "telescopic spear"
msgid_plural "telescopic spears"
msgstr[0] "伸縮矛"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'telescopic spear'}.
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "You collapse your spear."
msgstr "你收起了長矛。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'telescopic spear'}
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid ""
"A crude telescopic spear with a long and broad head and a primitive locking "
"mechanism. (A)ctivate to collapse and use it as a more suited for close "
"combat blade."
msgstr "一把帶有長寬矛頭和原始鎖定機制的粗製伸縮矛。(A)激活以收起並用作更適合近戰的刀刃。"

#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "telescopic spear (collapsed)"
msgid_plural "telescopic spear (collapsed)s"
msgstr[0] "伸縮矛（已收起）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'telescopic spear (collapsed)'}.
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "You extend your spear."
msgstr "你展開了長矛。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'telescopic spear (collapsed)'}
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "The spear is now collapsed and used as a chopping blade."
msgstr "長矛現已收起並用作劈砍刀刃。"

#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid "stone maul"
msgid_plural "stone mauls"
msgstr[0] "石錘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stone maul'}
#: .\mod_melee.json
msgid ""
"This is not a tool, but perhaps the most destructive stone weapon you can "
"make. Its long handle allows you to strike with a great momentum."
msgstr "這不是工具，但或許是你所能製作的最具破壞性的石制武器。其長柄允許你以巨大動量進行打擊。"

#: .\mod_tools_armor.json
msgid "visored helmet"
msgid_plural "visored helmets"
msgstr[0] "帶面甲頭盔"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'visored helmet'}.
#: .\mod_tools_armor.json
msgid "You open your visor"
msgstr "你打開了面甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'visored helmet'}
#: .\mod_tools_armor.json
msgid ""
"Helmet with openable visor. Not as thick and reliable as great helm due to "
"all moving parts. Use it to open the visor and catch your breath."
msgstr "帶有可開合面甲的頭盔。由於所有活動部件，不如巨盔厚實可靠。用它打開面甲以喘口氣。"

#: .\mod_tools_armor.json
msgid "visored helmet(open)"
msgid_plural "visored helmet(open)s"
msgstr[0] "帶面甲頭盔（打開）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'visored helmet(open)'}.
#: .\mod_tools_armor.json
msgid "You lower your visor"
msgstr "你放下了面甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'visored helmet(open)'}
#: .\mod_tools_armor.json
msgid ""
"Helmet with openable visor. Use it to close the visor to protect your face."
msgstr "帶有可開合面甲的頭盔。用它關閉面甲以保護你的臉部。"

#: .\mod_vehicles.json
msgid "Makeshift raft"
msgstr "臨時木筏"

#: .\mod_vehicles.json
msgid "Primitive canoe"
msgstr "原始獨木舟"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "More Makeshift Stuff"
msgstr "更多臨時物品"

#. ~ Description for More Makeshift Stuff
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds some more makeshift armors and weapons."
msgstr "添加更多臨時護甲和武器。"
